Peter Gale was dismissed by Nonsuch High School For Girls in Surrey for 'unprofessional and inappropriate conduct' He sent 'informal' emails to a sixth form pupil over a period of months . 
  Mail on Sunday investigation reveals he was dismissed two weeks ago . 
